>Description:
The two most used items in the last section of 
the Scheme menu is the items "Comment out with 
semicolons" and "Remove comments".

I propose to move them to the bottom of the
menu, in order to make them easier to access
using only the keyboard.

They will become

  Alt-c, <up>   and  Alt-c, <up>, <up>

in stead of

  Alt-c, <up> <up> <up> <up> and  Alt-c, <up>, <up>




